#

Vegan Classic Ukrainian Borscht

60 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Ukrainian

Course:

Main CourseSoup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup, packed with vegetables and infused with savory flavors, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 1 large, grated
  • potato: 1 large, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh dill: for garnish
